219153, "content": "思维", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069982}, {"id": 218388, "content": "数码产品，想买ipad pro或者surface pro！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 401513}, {"id": 218900, "content": "家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914818}, {"id": 218390, "content": "我自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068241}, {"id": 218392, "content": "国籍...", "image": null, "praise_count": 22, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134410}, {"id": 218393, "content": "内裤", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811728}, {"id": 218905, "content": "鼠标\n想要换的时候永远都是打游戏时，有空买的时候都忘了这茬。（打的懒都怪鼠标系列）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056169}, {"id": 219673, "content": "洗衣服", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240934}, {"id": 218394, "content": "牙膏等日用品一直都在用一个牌子的……", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1056357}, {"id": 219674, "content": "洗衣粉", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 240934}, {"id": 218395, "content": "我的那台用了五年额老爷机，每天都在用，每天都在不断吐槽：好卡好卡啊。然而没钱换。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641986}, {"id": 218396, "content": "我怕是活在一个死角里。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068287}, {"id": 218141, "content": "想不出来，能换的起的都换了，没换的都是换不起的", "image": null, "praise_count": 295, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251195}, {"id": 218397, "content": "化妆品", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 900556}, {"id": 218142, "content": "指甲钳，剪刀。", "image": null, "praise_count": 81, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1027999}, {"id": 218398, "content": "牙膏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068187}, {"id": 218654, "content": "各种小饰品嗄，那些特别可爱的小东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068920}, {"id": 218143, "content": "电动牙刷", "image": null, "praise_count": 35, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 653954}, {"id": 218655, "content": "各种小饰品嗄，那些小东西更可爱了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068920}, {"id": 218144, "content": "抹布", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 297429}, {"id": 218145, "content": "当初大二花了20块钱从在肯德基打工的舍友那里买的肯德基特惠活动蝙蝠侠水杯", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 847419}, {"id": 218146, "content": "手机壳 拖鞋", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 219170, "content": "AcFun", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 819634}, {"id": 218147, "content": "寝室的椅子", "image": null, "praise_count": 40, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}, {"id": 218403, "content": "电脑桌，坐着总不合适，结果一用就是十年了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1243446}, {"id": 218404, "content": "大致翻了一下，居然没有说钥匙扣，这个需求可以有啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015515}, {"id": 219428, "content": "杯子，一个特百惠杯子用了五年", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070424}, {"id": 231716, "content": "牙签", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 218149, "content": "沙发", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1067847}, {"id": 218150, "content": "手机壳", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037363}, {"id": 218406, "content": "牙膏", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068296}, {"id": 218662, "content": "眼镜哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1068929}, {"id": 218151, "content": "没有死角，什么都可以升级", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0